   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Give Rural Women Group Modern Shea Butter Centre</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will complete the construction two Shea butter processing Centres to serve women in two cluster rural communities in the Bole district of Ghana.  The  project will provide  rural women  opportunity for off season livelihood diversification strategy, increase production efficiency and effectiveness and incomes through the use of improved technology to reduce their climate change vulnerability to guarantee long term livelihood improvement.</narrative>
  </description>
